        "created_at": "2025-03-31T09:39:10.665Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi, I might be a bit late to help you, but have you been inputting the Signal PIN? If so, try using your phone PIN instead. For me, it asks for the phone password, not the signal PIN.<br>\nHowever, if the UI message is confusing for people using a PIN to unlock their phone and not a password, it might be a good idea in general to change that message to make this clear. Can you provide a screenshot of what the PIN request looks like?</p>",
